---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/CommonPage.astro'

import { Comment } from '@/components/advanced'
import { Aside, Button, InfoCard } from '@/components/user'

export const prerender = true

const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: 'project-description', text: '项目说明' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'usage-instructions', text: '使用说明' },
  { depth: 2, slug: 'self-hosting', text: '自行部署' }
]
---

<PageLayout
  title='PKU Treehole Starred Saver'
  headings={headings}
  info={{ slug: '/projects/treehole', hideComment: false }}
>
  <div class='treehole-page mx-auto space-y-8'>
    <section class='space-y-3'>
      <h2 id='project-description'>项目说明</h2>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>帮助北京大学的同学下载自己在树洞中收藏的帖子, 留作纪念.</p>
      <Aside type='tip' title='部署状态'>
        后端 API 服务已于 2026.04.10 下线, 当前页面保留项目说明和自行部署入口.
      </Aside>
      <div class='flex flex-wrap gap-3'>
        <Button
          title='GitHub Repository'
          href='https://github.com/EmptyBlueBox/PKU_Treehole_Starred_Saver'
          style='ahead'
        />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class='space-y-3'>
      <h2 id='usage-instructions'>使用说明</h2>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground'>
        自行部署后, 每次运行会得到一个以时间戳和用户 ID 命名的文件夹.
      </p>
      <pre
        class='overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-muted p-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
  .
  └── TimeStamp-YourUserID
      ├── Image
      │   ├── 1500000.gif
      │   └── 7508259.jpeg
      ├── RawJson
      │   └── TimeStamp.json
      ├── 1500000.md
      ├── 7508259.md
      └── 7541521.md
    </pre>
      <ul class='list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-muted-foreground'>
        <li><strong>Image</strong> 收藏帖子中的图片, 按帖子编号命名.</li>
        <li><strong>RawJson</strong> 原始 JSON 数据, 便于后续处理.</li>
        <li><strong>Markdown</strong> 每个收藏帖会生成一个 Markdown 文件.</li>
      </ul>
      <figure class='space-y-2'>
        <img
          src='https://cdn.lyt0112.com/2025/07/95d65ac40a0890406bc99f9cf87d5c3e.png'
          alt='Generated Markdown file example'
          class='mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-3xl rounded-md border border-border'
          loading='lazy'
        />
        <figcaption class='text-center text-sm italic text-muted-foreground'>
          生成的 Markdown 文件示例
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class='space-y-2'>
        <img
          src='https://cdn.lyt0112.com/2025/07/a6c4b036100c206cfe90abf1aef4096a.png'
          alt='Reference format example'
          class='mx-auto h-auto w-full max-w-3xl rounded-md border border-border'
          loading='lazy'
        />
        <figcaption class='text-center text-sm italic text-muted-foreground'>
          引用格式示例
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
    </section>

    <section class='space-y-3'>
      <h2 id='self-hosting'>自行部署</h2>
      <Aside type='note' title='开源说明'>
        项目代码托管在 GitHub, 可自行部署后使用. 页面不再提供账号登录和数据收集服务.
      </Aside>
      <Aside type='danger' title='隐私说明'>
        自行部署时请确认服务只在可信环境中运行, 账号, 密码和验证码仅用于登录树洞.
      </Aside>
    </section>
  </div>
  <br />
  <Comment />
</PageLayout>
